<ITEM><HI>Morrice,</HI> &mdash;, made &s;ecretary of &s;tate, i. 4. His character, 5. Retires from office, 108.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Mulgrave,</HI> Earl of, made governor of Hull, i. 280. Is created Marquis of Normanby, ii. 62.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Mun&s;ter,</HI> Bi&s;hop of, joins the Engli&s;h, i. 74. And makes an irruption into the territories of the States, 75.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Murray,</HI> Captain, &s;ent by the court of St. Germains, with Captain Simon Fra&s;er, to Scotland, ii. 265.</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Mu&s;kerry,</HI> Lord, &s;lain in the fir&s;t Dutch war, i. 70.</ITEM>
